1
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:17,079
I was careless.

2
00:00:18,039 --> 00:00:20,120
I thought you could treat your own wound.

3
00:00:21,239 --> 00:00:22,079
The poison has gone too deep.

4
00:00:22,559 --> 00:00:23,320
Your pulse is chaotic.

5
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,760
Their fingernails were coated with poison.

6
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:30,039
If the poison reaches your organs...

7
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,520
I need to examine your wound.

8
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:51,280
Let me suck the poison out for you.

9
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:04,760
This is the place.

10
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,079
This is where the old poison master lives.

11
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,280
I don't dare go in.

12
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,080
I'm heading back now.

13
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,439
The Death Gate

14
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,599
No trespassing for the living

15
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:46,439
Enter alive, leave dead

16
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,199
You've got some skills.

17
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,840
Death's Door doesn't let the living pass

18
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,800
Careful, it's poisonous

19
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,039
Master Zhang

20
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,360
Young Master

21
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,759
It's you

22
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,280
It's really you

23
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:13,719
Master Zhang

24
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:19,960
Yueyue

25
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,520
Grandpa

26
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,400
Master Zhang

27
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,919
Why are you here?

28
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:35,439
Wang threatened my granddaughter's life

29
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,199
and imprisoned me here

30
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:39,680
I've been barely surviving ever since

31
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,919
So it really was the Wang family

32
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:45,560
So the prescription is with you?

33
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:47,560
What exactly is this formula?

34
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,080
It's the one

35
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,599
you developed years ago

36
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,120
from that half of an ancient formula

37
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,639
What did you say?

38
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,520
Wait a moment

39
00:04:00,879 --> 00:04:01,479
I'll bring it over

40
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,439
This is the formula

41
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:27,920
Inspired by old texts and half a formula

42
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,360
I devoted myself to developing this one

43
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,160
Hoping to create

44
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,439
a miracle cure for critical illnesses

45
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,000
But this formula is dangerous

46
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,120
It's a way to fight poison with poison

47
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,639
An unorthodox method

48
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,560
So...

49
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,199
So your parents

50
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,759
wouldn't let you keep researching it

51
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,319
Feifan

52
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:51,160
Stop researching this formula

53
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,920
This formula

54
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,279
No one has cracked it in over a century

55
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,720
If you can perfect it

56
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,639
it can truly work miracles and save lives

57
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,399
But if you fail

58
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,279
it becomes a deadly poison

59
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:04,360
Mom

60
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,319
But these few ingredients...

61
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,160
How could I possibly fail?

62
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,600
It could poison someone to death

63
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:08,920
Stop researching it

64
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,199
Fine

65
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:09,680
Let's go

66
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,639
What are you doing?

67
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,120
Taking you back to rest

68
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:13,879
I won't research it anymore, Mom

69
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,959
Don't research it

70
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:15,720
I know, I know

71
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,519
I told you to study medicine broadly

72
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,959
to read more medical books

73
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,000
not to research this dangerous formula

74
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:27,519
If made wrong, it becomes a deadly weapon

75
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,480
You're a doctor

76
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:30,800
You save lives

77
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,480
You

78
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,279
Go copy the medical books

79
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,639
A hundred times

80
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,160
So it was my formula

81
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:42,319
that got my parents killed

82
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,560
If I hadn't insisted back then

83
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,120
on researching this formula

84
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:48,680
my parents...

85
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,199
What's done is done

86
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,639
Don't blame yourself

87
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,279
Careful now.

88
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:04,720
You okay?

89
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,759
I can manage on my own.

90
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,120
You're still injured too.

91
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,120
Let me help.

92
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:10,279
Come on.

93
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,240
Xu Ruojin.

94
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:22,160
You still think you're qualified

95
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,759
to keep fighting me over Feifan?

96
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:32,959
I want to go home.

97
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:33,639
No, you can't.

98
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,439
Master says to rest at the sanatorium.

99
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,839
This is my real home.

100
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:37,600
I want to go home.

101
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,120
You really can't.

102
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,160
Your top priority right now

103
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,759
is to fully recover.

104
00:06:40,759 --> 00:06:41,439
Ren Ran.

105
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,199
Master.

106
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,519
Brother.

107
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,639
Why are you back?

108
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,079
When did you get back?

109
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,160
I just snuck out.

110
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,360
Always full of excuses.

111
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,439
Come, let me take a look.

112
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,560
Alright.

113
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,600
You're pretty much healed anyway.

114
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,680
Since you're back, so be it.

115
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,879
Come on, let's go home.

116
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,079
Brother.

117
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,199
What is it?

118
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,199
I want to reopen Premier Medical Hall.

119
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,279
Master Zhang.

120
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,720
What do you think?

121
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,079
Yes.

122
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:21,920
Since you're back,

123
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,759
we should reopen Premier Medical Hall.

124
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,040
Let's go.

125
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:44,800
Feifan.

126
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,360
Brother.

127
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:49,879
Brother.

128
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,040
I plan to reopen Premier Medical Hall.

129
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,639
Reopen Premier Medical Hall?

130
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,720
Did you find any leads in Lijia Village?

131
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,639
I found a few things.

132
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:08,720
Wang Wenhao took my old formula.

133
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:12,360
For years, the Wangs made drugs from it,

134
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,240
but none of them succeeded.

135
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:17,639
So what's your next move?

136
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:19,759
Feifan.

137
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:22,160
If there's anything I can help with,

138
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,839
you just have to ask.

139
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:32,200
There actually is something I need your help with.

140
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,639
Tell me.

141
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,399
The thing is,

142
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,000
about reopening Premier Medical Hall,

143
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,919
Ren Ran is still an amateur,

144
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,080
and Master Zhang is getting on in years.

145
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,120
When I'm tied up at the hospital,

146
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,120
so sometimes,

147
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,240
I'll need you to fill in for me.

148
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,720
Of course, no problem.

149
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,240
Well then,

150
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,480
I still have things at the hospital,

151
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:55,639
so I'll get going.

152
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,039
Okay, sure.

153
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,399
Hey, Shen Yue.

154
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,679
Ren Feifan.

155
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,799
Did you forget what you promised me?

156
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,960
Your liver fire is a bit excessive.

157
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,960
Want me to help balance it out?

158
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,000
Balance it out?

159
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:29,639
If you keep your promise to me,

160
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,840
I'll heal on my own, no medicine needed.

161
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,960
You have the evidence from Lijia Village.

162
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:37,360
Why haven't you put those scumbags away?

163
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:41,320
What if I want to drag the Wangs in too?

164
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,399
What do you mean?

165
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,279
Take a look at this file first.

166
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:54,639
Beishi Pharma Museum Partnership Project.

167
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:57,159
It's a small project,

168
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,799
but it's backed by the government.

169
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:04,120
An exclusive government partnership.

170
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,519
This...

171
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,559
is my bait.

172
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,960
So you...

173
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,559
I want to let them fight it out.

174
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,799
You can set up a meeting with your grandfather now.

175
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:23,519
Master.

176
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,720
We've got a tough case back home.

177
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,320
Ren Ran told me to rush you back right away.

178
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:28,200
Let's go.

179
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:29,000
Come on.

180
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:31,720
Here's your ball.

181
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,399
Daddy!

182
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:34,440
Daddy!

183
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,639
Kid, you've got the wrong person.

184
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,679
I'm not your daddy.

185
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,720
Exactly.

186
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,399
I'm really not your daddy.

187
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,240
Did you get separated from your family?

188
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,840
Sorry about that.

189
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,879
The kid ran off too fast.

190
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:48,240
Yixin, let's go home with auntie.

191
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,960
Yixin wants to go home with Daddy.

192
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,399
Hurry on back now.

193
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:52,639
Your family must be worried.

194
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,600
Master.

195
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,240
You know what?

196
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,960
The kid does look a bit like you.

197
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:03,120
Didn't you say Ren Ran was in a hurry?

198
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,759
Then let's get moving.

199
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,240
Go, go, go.

200
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:07,679
An ex-convict...

201
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,320
Why should I talk business with you?

202
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:12,960
Elder Li.

203
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,960
Please take a look at this contract first.

204
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,080
Wanli Pill.

205
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:24,000
Good.

206
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,279
It really is fine medicine.

207
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:31,200
Your backers want the northern market?

208
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:31,639
Correct.

209
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:33,679
Then why come to me?

210
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:35,720
For anyone else,

211
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,919
there might be many options.

212
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:39,080
After all,

213
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:42,759
The Wangs and Xus dominate the market.

214
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:45,000
But for me,

215
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,919
you're the only choice.

216
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,759
The Wangs murdered my parents.

217
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:54,120
The Xus have the woman who betrayed me.

218
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,879
If you were in my shoes,

219
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,799
would you choose them?

220
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,120
Good.

221
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,840
So how do we split it?

222
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,000
Four-four-two.

223
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:09,840
You get four.

224
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:10,879
She gets four.

225
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:12,080
I get two.

226
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,480
Not bad.

227
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,480
Very sincere.

228
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:17,519
So when do we sign the contract?

229
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,679
Don't be in such a rush.

230
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,799
The reason you get forty percent

231
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,639
comes with a few requirements.

232
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:26,399
And exactly because I can't meet them

233
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,919
that you get forty percent.

234
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:32,799
Wh-what requirements?

235
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,720
Don't be nervous.

236
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,399
These requirements are very simple for you.

237
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:37,679
First,

238
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:40,279
a company in Beishi's Pharma Association.

239
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:41,200
Second,

240
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:44,440
capable of producing 25 rare herbs.

241
00:12:45,159 --> 00:12:45,600
Third,

242
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:49,519
with an exclusive government partnership.

243
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,080
Meaning, with government endorsement

244
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:55,039
in exclusive cooperation with your company.

245
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,480
Do you have that?

246
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:00,320
Yes.

247
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:02,639
We've often worked with the government.

248
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,759
As for exclusive, I'll go check.

249
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,399
How long do you need?

250
00:13:09,639 --> 00:13:10,200
One month.

251
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:11,679
Yes, yes, yes.

252
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,559
One month.

253
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,519
One month.

254
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,320
All right.

255
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:16,159
Then I'll wait for your good news.

256
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,639
Pleasure doing business.

257
00:13:30,759 --> 00:13:31,360
Miss Su.

258
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,320
If it isn't Miss Su.

259
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,240
You've got the wrong person.

260
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,039
No way.

261
00:13:35,039 --> 00:13:36,879
Last time, we dined with Editor Li.

262
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,639
Miss Su's face,

263
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:38,960
right now I...

264
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,200
I said, you've got the wrong person.

265
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:40,919
Come on.

266
00:13:41,519 --> 00:13:43,200
You still owe me a kiss from last time.

267
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,840
Time to pay up now, isn't it?

268
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:46,440
Pay up, huh?

269
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,200
Damn bitch, you're asking for it!
